      "description": "This 996 Turbo is a superlative example of the legendary Mezger-designed 3.6L flat-six. The twin-turbocharged powerplant delivers linear boost through a flawlessly synchronized six-speed manual gearbox. Mechanical integrity is paramount, featuring a factory dry-sump lubrication system and an unmolested AWD drivetrain. Recent service includes a comprehensive borescope inspection, pinning of the coolant pipes for long-term reliability, and new Bosch coil packs. The suspension remains taut with factory-spec Bilstein dampers, while the four-piston monoblock calipers provide immediate, fade-free deceleration. This is a collector-grade chassis with zero parasitic draw and a pristine underbody.",
